&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.gpg4win.org/&#34; title=&#34;Gpg4win - Secure email and file encryption with GnuPG for Windows&#34;&gt;Gpg4win&lt;/a&gt; 3.1.0 の構成は以下の通り。&lt;/p&gt;

